    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape that it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping it spotless and well-loved\u2014it\u2019s been my pride and joy. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better than the photos. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without that dealership headache, this is the one for you! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
