      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, an icon of the JDM golden era. This example features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering a seamless power curve through its five-speed manual gearbox. The front-midship layout ensures a perfect 50:50 weight distribution, complemented by a lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for unparalleled lateral grip. This unmolested specimen boasts factory-original paint and an immaculate cockpit, with all vacuum lines and cooling components meticulously maintained to prevent heat soak. Compression is verified high across all rotor faces, ensuring the integrity of the apex seals. A true collector-grade FD for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
