      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, having been exclusively garage-kept and professionally detailed on a regular schedule. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather upholstery is supple and retains its original scent, while every technological feature and button operates with factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive, open-checkbook service history performed strictly by master technicians. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
